          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1681209090894-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi half[ves]</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 2-3 min or until softened</p>",
