          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the halloumi is cooking, slice your <strong>gluten-free</strong> <strong>brioche bun[s] </strong>horizontally through the middle and reassemble on a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until toasted</p>",
